$!!		nodes in cofig.dat if there were more than two nodes.
$!!	27-sep-2005 (devjo01) b115278
$!!		Remove cluster_max_node.
$!!     26-oct-2005 (devjo01) b115463
$!!		Remove MEMORY and ADMIN node specific sub-directories,
